{"tid":1222700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［支持香港警察既文宣組入］暴徒係要打！不服來辯！","createTime":"2019-06-14T13:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:31:19.000Z","uid":258340,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bff373feb3e5be672c3c598d2bceaa2d38871aa0","tid":1222700,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"佢地根本無做錯 <br />\n佢地就好似慈母咁<br />\n只係教導緊你班任性既孩子<br />\n我依家就要向公務員事務局表揚香港警察！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢聽到有公務員講：<br />\n搵人寫封信去公務員事務局<br />\n投訴警察開槍 過份使用武力 執法不公<br />\n記得要Fax去<br />\n留個email<br />\n之後會有人跟進<br />\n勁撚過警監會好多<br />\n<br />\n真心 我唔可以再講<br />\n加油各位<br />\n我地成層同事都支持你地<br />\n<br />\n搵英文好既寫<br />\n如果只知中文名<br />\n就（XXX)咁寫<br />\n送未過試用期警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等住無得撈 加刑事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未過試用期警察 多數88<br />\n仲要開槍條個位 都未做夠三年<br />\n報串上去公務員事務局<br />\n可以88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊制既公務員 隨時連退休金都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得寫清楚 警察名 同編號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nEmail + Fax 最有效<br />\n<br />\n以上都係發夢有人講<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以打份sample出黎 <br />\n比香港人齊齊向公務員事務局表揚香港警察！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">公 務 員 事 務 局<br />\n<br />\n投 訴 組<br />\n電 話： 2810 3446<br />\n傳 真： 2868 5069<br />\n電 郵： csbcomp@csb.gov.hk</span>"},{"pid":"7a7daa5d144ff263b94060aea4fe94d8cc9cf383","tid":1222700,"uid":258340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb92a39e7fe5cd138a6904c0dff8bf7773beb4f","tid":1222700,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"支持香港警察！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b229e9c7ab63d6fc2400756477c16f86c9746cc6","tid":1222700,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee1932954789714e25a23b4f64f7c6d05b94e7a","tid":1222700,"uid":38804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3aec4da953efa97ec500e8117e2a48234398920","tid":1222700,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6341c258ea0fb7cc90156a7d107465dd9d055ea3","tid":1222700,"uid":28852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}